kaifu 58 is not expected to propose any major trade or 
diplomatic initiatives in his talks friday with president bush 
but he hopes to establish a close and credible working 
relationship with the president and other american leaders said 
yukio okamoto director of the foreign ministrys first north 
america division 
kaifu also will use the 12day tour which will take him to 
