<TEXT>
cholera has broken out at a camp housing 4500 
vietnamese refugees who suffer from poor sanitary conditions and 
lack of water a health official said wednesday 
the first case of the disease was discovered sunday the same day 
food riots hit the camp 
dr lo waikee principal medical officer of the vietnamese boat 
